Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.12,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}相聚一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:14.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我想打从心里大叫一句 好想快点见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:28.66,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我相信总有一天 一定能相遇相知永结连理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:44.01,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}起步走出 希望你能追着我的背影而来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.33,0:00:57.85,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我孤单一人只为等候你的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.14,0:01:04.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}落英缤纷的春日午后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:12.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}我将祈祷转为誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.44,0:01:27.05,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85}但愿你不会忘记最重要的事 永远闪亮动人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.37,0:01:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,你要把伊吹…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神,你也跟你爸爸一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代老师,你为什么不接受呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说,我非常渴望这封介绍信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.15,0:01:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我真的无法收下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怕自己会这样随波逐流下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就业的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.33,0:01:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要自己决定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟这是我自己的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.70,0:02:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#78这是秘密! 五代的打工奋斗记!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.85,0:02:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-赖皮,一对一根本打不赢… -大哥哥的身体比较大…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,那你们一起上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.86,0:02:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油,加油…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.07,0:02:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我录取了,我录取了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被阳炎产业录取了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神部长的介绍信真的很有效
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.18,0:02:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的收下那封介绍信了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.48,0:02:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.85,0:02:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你了,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.35,0:03:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧,你连这种事都不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-人家真的不知道嘛 -真是够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊吹在家的感觉果然很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,这一个月真是漫长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.72,0:03:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,五代他为什么说 不要那封介绍信呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道,我才懒得理那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他的关系 给我添了多少麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也应该很清楚才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了,这种时候不要谈他的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,他说要自己决定 这是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能觉得我对他是个负担吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:04:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代老师可能觉得很累
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:03.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为八神很专情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再去找他确认一下如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定他现在很后悔 自己说出那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,你连离家出走都做了 再去找他确认一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.90,0:04:21.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么好喝的啤酒 是考上大学以来的第二次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.71,0:04:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是败给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然硬向八神部长 要来那封介绍信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然罗,我可是拼了命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错过这种大好机会 不会有第二次了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:48.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问你,你是不是后悔了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事后恨我,我也不管你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也才不管你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一那家公司又倒闭了 哭死了我也不管
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳炎产业,听起来就像是一家 快要消失的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.11,0:05:05.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本,我是开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神她爸爸也说过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是慎重选择的 绝对不会倒闭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.29,0:05:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还保证呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,今晚要喝个痛快 全部我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥,啤酒尽管拿过来 再来个五、六瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有烧酒加柠檬,乌龙茶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:35.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓,番茄,哈蜜瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青苹果,梅子,柳橙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.75,0:05:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小黄瓜,酪梨,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:41.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有,开一瓶威士忌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥,再来一瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.97,0:06:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你在干嘛,快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦,马上来,马上来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,五代…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:19.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说阪本找到工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以跑去喝酒 今晚说不定不回来?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,他还真悠哉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.64,0:06:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢光临,欢迎再来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,再去喝一家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要喝一家啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:49.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是去酒家啦,酒家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有认识的人在那里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.55,0:06:53.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他帮我们 介绍几个漂亮美眉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的很喜欢“介绍”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.63,0:06:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,庆祝大学生找到工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里再来四瓶啤酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.38,0:07:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外加一盘花枝拼盘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.81,0:07:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,帅哥,你好大方喔 你会出人头地喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的罗 这家伙的后台可是很有力的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代到底在想什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.38,0:07:50.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果昨天晚上没回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为要帮阪本庆祝找到工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是没错啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是他有时间帮别人庆祝吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.02,0:08:00.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是太悠哉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.19,0:08:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟这种男人结婚会吃苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会吃苦我是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作是一辈子的事 还是慢慢找比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.70,0:08:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还慢慢找?都已经10月了耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初应该收下那封介绍信的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那封介绍信 就算没优点的五代也能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.34,0:08:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代他也很努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.27,0:08:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门没锁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.07,0:08:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,臭死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还在睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.45,0:09:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!给我起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.82,0:09:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.82,0:09:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还敢问! 你要睡到什么时候!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭冈先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么,你这家伙真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点起来准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.16,0:09:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.57,0:09:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少跟我装蒜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.97,0:09:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天不是说好了吗 钱不够的部分用打工来偿还
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗?我不记得有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不对?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少跟我来这一套
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.78,0:09:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点,快点 不用换衣服了,穿这样就好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.28,0:09:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你要去哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还用问吗?当然是去幼稚园啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴,你不要给我说梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八神,结果怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他请假没来上班
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.54,0:10:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么,人家特地来找他耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是去找工作了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道,好像没有打电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是生病了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生车祸?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.36,0:10:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被绑架了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好,在酒钱还清之前 我会好好锻链你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.81,0:10:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先做好心理准备喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是,请多指教 -是,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太小声了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-请多指教! -请多指教!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好,接客的时候 要面带开朗笑容,口齿清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是,接客的时候 要面带开朗笑容,口齿清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好,这句话要牢牢记住喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.76,0:10:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这是我们公司的社训
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.93,0:10:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:10:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来到公司外面 展开实地训练
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公司外面?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实地训练?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,这位老板
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有折价优待 可以享受极乐气氛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要进来看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟,不要这么说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.29,0:11:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是出来找乐子的,不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.49,0:11:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来,带两位里面坐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.36,0:11:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好棒喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,你们两个也试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-啊? -啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.90,0:11:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊你个头啦,快去试试看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.00,0:11:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是笨头笨脑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.07,0:11:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能照着他的话做了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦?出声拉客啊,出声
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.91,0:11:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这间酒家正在打折优待…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这间酒家,正在打折优待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.22,0:11:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:11:59.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找情侣干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你的态度干嘛阴沉沉的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.10,0:12:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么 你看看阪本,他就做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,要不要进来坐一坐啊 有漂亮的美眉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.11,0:12:12.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎哟,不要走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,不用拉我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,阪本,这位是常客
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好您好,阳炎产业的总经理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.89,0:12:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来来,请进请进 丽莎在等你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阳炎产业不就是你要去的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不妙吧,听说他是常客耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我把五代放在这里抵债
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:54.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.25,0:12:55.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.02,0:13:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想溜吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作找得还顺利吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:37.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好 今天也想去就职课看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,真的很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很累的样子 不要紧吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.19,0:13:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事,我不要紧的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:14:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我明明没必要说谎的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.81,0:14:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八…八神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.94,0:14:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,你不是生病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么这么问?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.77,0:14:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我昨天去幼稚园 你请假没上班
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊,不过你看 我没生病好好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.28,0:14:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代老师,你找工作还顺利吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.56,0:14:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉,我没什么时间
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有很重要的事要去办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:14:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.54,0:15:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦,那改天再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.68,0:15:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道他真的觉得我是个负担吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接客的时候 要面带开朗笑容,口齿清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接客的时候 要面带开朗笑容,口齿清晰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好,今天也提起精神,好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.88,0:15:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.71,0:15:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊,请进请进 折价大优待喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.15,0:15:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊,请进请进
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,老板 漂亮的美眉在等着你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在折价大优待 喝到饱,吃到饱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:58.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你也表现得很不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗? 因为我得连阪本的份一起努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥,了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:10.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还谈不上了不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.34,0:16:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经自暴自弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.34,0:16:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,有年轻漂亮的美眉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在喝酒唱歌都超便宜的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,这位老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.05,0:16:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.66,0:16:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.07,0:16:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛逃走 快点带他进去,带他进去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请带我进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你是五代的邻居啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这要好好服务一下才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看是要吃水果还是开整瓶酒 尽管叫没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.31,0:16:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正五代请客嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:17:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托,我几时说过要请客了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然叫她干嘛?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没去找工作 跑来酒家打工的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道要我告诉她吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来,再拿五、六瓶酒来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚要喝到打烊为止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-哇,好棒喔 -我可以叫水果切盘吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,你答应我的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.76,0:17:36.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能告诉管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.06,0:17:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你烦不烦啊 难道你不相信我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘,开门小声一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,你偷偷摸摸在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧 绝对不能告诉管理员…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:10.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们一起回来啊 真是稀奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:16.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,因为五代在酒…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-四谷! -鱼子酱真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喝醉了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:24.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是伤脑筋,居然醉成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:27.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走,上楼去吧,上楼去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.64,0:18:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天去就职课问得怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心,他等于找到工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是餐饮服务业,对不对?五代
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.73,0:18:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,睡觉去,睡觉去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟我一起睡吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡扯什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是找工作找得不顺利 所以没有脸见八神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.78,0:19:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.68,0:19:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他好像很想摆脱八神 情况不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管别人怎么说都无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正八神一定要看到 五代老师顺利就业
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.72,0:19:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则她是不会放手的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.33,0:19:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好专情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊,快来啊快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只限今天特别大优待
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.57,0:19:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,现在折价大优待 可以享受极乐气氛喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.11,0:19:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗?可以喝免费的酒?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,我有朋友在这里工作
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪,那不是五代吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.75,0:19:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这种地方做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,这跟我们说好的不一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧,我没有跟管理员 透露只字片语
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:08.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,真的可以 从你的薪水里扣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代也来喝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.71,0:20:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知不知道这是谁出的钱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美小姐,朱美小姐 请转台至六号桌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美,你几岁了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,17岁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.09,0:20:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.26,0:20:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,我才是朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.10,0:20:34.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这套制服好可爱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想穿穿看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:37.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿了一定很好看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家好高兴喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.54,0:20:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我也来这里工作好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:53.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,竟然全来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.76,0:20:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干脆把这件事向管理员说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我还跟她说 我是出门去找工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.17,0:21:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,谢谢你的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要早点回来喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.94,0:21:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.11,0:21:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事绝对不能告诉管理员喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.68,0:21:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.05,0:21:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便帮你敷衍一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最不会敷衍了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我也不太会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了 该说的时候我自己会说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是这样我们会过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.26,0:21:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说嘛,每晚都让他请客 多不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.50,0:21:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们每晚都想来勒索我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:41.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌,你怎么说得这么难听
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我们已经上了同一条船
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.41,0:21:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.11,0:21:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:53.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.18,0:21:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:21:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚没跟五代一起回来吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:22:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道耶 他可能忙着到处找工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,头上绑着一条黄带子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.56,0:22:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在笑什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.36,0:22:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来来,管理员也来喝一杯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐啊,坐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.50,0:22:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是坐在这里喝酒…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系 大家来祝五代顺利就业
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.04,0:22:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.44,0:22:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干杯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.34,0:22:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊,快来啊快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:25.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃到饱,喝到饱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美小姐,朱美小姐 请转台至六号桌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.15,0:22:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.40,0:22:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.03,0:22:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我工作一向都是很认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.93,0:22:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会知道!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我就这么倒楣 老是碰到这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.91,0:22:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.21,0:22:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也这么认为吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.71,0:22:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢,一共两千八百块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱…钱不够
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.67,0:23:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊,快来啊快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃又便宜喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.84,0:23:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,过来尝尝看吧 好吃的黑轮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你蛮厉害的嘛 还剩五百块,好好加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.65,0:23:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你别看我这样 我可是这方面的专家喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,那位老板 快来吃好吃的黑轮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.52,0:23:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来啊,快来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.69,0:23:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃的黑轮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.49,0:23:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快来吃啊,快来吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.03,0:23:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板,老板…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.02,0:23:46.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.56,0:23:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼稚园的工作被炒鱿鱼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.33,0:23:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,顶级的爱情便当呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.93,0:23:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在哪里吃呢?用什么表情吃呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.77,0:23:59.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像个男子汉从实招来吧 五代
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.27,0:23:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.80,0:24:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“响子对不起! 含泪的爱妻便当?”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.91,0:24:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过,酒家的工作不要辞掉喔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.17,0:24:07.17,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.98,0:24:15.71,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}Begin the night Begin your love
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.99,0:24:28.64,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}你该知道这不是擦身而过的恋情 亲吻也是…woo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.17,0:24:46.66,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}你比我想像中冷淡 喜欢一个人独处 沉默不语
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.94,0:24:57.42,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}不要逞强 在这烛火依偎着的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.83,0:25:14.85,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}凝视着你的一切 试着将至今的谎言吹熄
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.55,0:25:22.11,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}Begin the night Begin your love
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.39,0:25:34.50,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx88}自我陶醉故弄玄虚 对我行不通…woo

